frames.text: Settlers convoy Selenium-XII left Tau Ceti e on January  14th  3051, boarding 120 civilians on a journey to 94 Ceti b and the founding of a new colony.
Jack Chems, pathfinder squad captain, is in charge of leading the way of the convoy through the galaxy.
A few million kilometers ahead of its MotherShip, Jack Chems and his squad are sent gathering datas concerning an asteroid field from which unknown signals have been spotted.
